posts.description: Today I want you to be positive. Now, that doesn't mean SMILE AND BE HAPPY, some of us have probably had a bad start to the morning😂 (like me). What I mean is, today if you hear someone say something negative, rather than responding with a negative, I want you to try and find something POSITIVE that you can respond with! Watch how different your mood becomes when you actually FOCUS on the GOOD things in life. www.kaylaitsines.com/app

If someone is bullying you, putting you down or hurting your feelings, don't ever wonder "what is wrong with me?". Instead, think "what happened to that person for them to act this way?". There is a chance that the person who is bothering you actually has a problem with themselves! Hold your head high, stick to your morals and don't let negative people affect you! You deserve better.  www.kaylaitsines.com/app #bbg

Just having a little moment of refection. I feel like the last few years has been an absolute whirlwind! When life gets busy, you often don't get the chance to stop and think about what you've achieved along the way! Time is passing by no matter what you do. So why stress? Why get worked up? Why worry so much when you can be happy and enjoy your life instead! I know that's easier said than done sometimes, but really when you think about it, you SHOULD be happy. You should be able to celebrate every moment. Time will pass no matter what.....so you may as well be happy and do what you love. www.kaylaitsines.com/app #bbg
